[PROPRIETARY MODEL PLACEHOLDER]

This location is reserved for the serialized Machine Learning/Deep Learning model 
developed as part of research at the University of Florida. 

MODEL SPECIFICATIONS:
- Data Source: NeoSpectra NIR Spectroscopy
- Spectral Range: 1350 – 2500 nm
- Training Library: 700+ EAA Histosol samples
- Targeted Indicators: Soil Carbon Stability and Health Parameters

The calibrated .joblib file containing the final model weights and coefficients 
will be released to this public repository following peer-review and 
formal academic publication.
